Overview



Introducing the NCR SelfServ 80 Series ATM FamilyThe NCR SelfServ 80 Series is a new range of ATMs that enable financial institutions to grow revenue, reduce cost, manage risk and enhance the customer experience. They deliver a new generation of omni-channel self-service experiences at the ATM – built on the following key principles:





Transform - transform self-service banking for the future
Attract - let your brand’s personality break through
Engage - make connections that create experiences
Secure - maintain the trust and integrity of your transactions and your network
Manage - use the right solutions and processes for efficient systems management
Available - stay connected, serve more customers

The SelfServ ATM Family consists of the following:
						
Cash Dispensers - SelfServ 23 and 27 are interior lobby and exterior through the wall premium cash dispensers 
Recycling ATMs – SelfServ 83 and 87 are interior lobby and exterior through the wall single function recyclers
Multifunction ATMs - The SelfServ 80 Series is the most recent addition to the Family and consists of robust range of multifunctional ATMs completing our SelfServ portfolio




SelfServ 80 Series Core Values



Transform
Branch transformation and improving the customer experience are at the heart of NCR’s SelfServ 80 Series. For consumers, the ATM interface now supports multi-touch and is enabled for many other omni-channel interactions. These ATMs transform the self-service channel by putting the personal touch back into banking, through fully configurable interactive and assisted service capabilities along with modern design and aesthetics.  The SelfServ 80 Series enables you to connect with consumers the way they prefer, anywhere, anytime.




Attract
These ATMs help financial institutions project a positive brand image through design features such as dynamic colour LEDs and customizable branding panels. Additionally, NCR’s market leading software delivers highly personalized and efficient experiences for consumers.  Leveraging the power of NCR Connections  software to deliver highly-differentiated and personalized experiences, with tailored marketing and promotional offers at the ATM.




Manage
The SelfServ 80 Series enables financial institutions to manage ATM networks with intelligence and efficiency. NCR understands the importance of managing your network and we offer the right solutions and processes to help you improve the performance of your entire ATM network. The SelfServ 80 Series enables faster fault detection and resolution, and features state of health indicators across all Media Handling 2.0 devices allowing you to improve performance and manage risk while reducing costs.




Engage
The SelfServ 80 Series ATMs give you the power to engage and build connections that create experiences for consumers. The design and aesthetics of the SelfServ 80 Series have been combined with enhanced interactivity using multi-touch capabilities. NCR gives you the power to shift to new interaction and authentication models at the ATM, such as; multi-touch, contactless, and mobile prestaging, which support the omni-channel mobile-first customer. These ATMs also allow you to tailor your marketing messaging based on the individual preferences of the consumer. Location and time-based targeted marketing allows you to engage with your customers on a new level.




Available
Your ATMs must be available at all times. Customers today are convenience and time oriented. They expect to access their financial institution whenever and wherever they want. Many of the SelfServ 80 Series ATMs offer an increase in cassette capacity as well as deposit and dispense size to ensure your network can serve your customers where and when they demand.  The SelfServ 80 Series features:

S2 dispenser - designed to provide greater cash capacity and higher reliability at the ATM.
GBXX2 module - to drive performance improvements and uptime in the area of recycling.
SDM2 - designed to deliver fast and simplified mixed media deposit in a single transaction, with great mixed media handing standards.





Secure
Security is a major concern for every bank customer. The SelfServ 80 Series has security "designed in" to respond to the latest threats. The flush, infinity glass enhances security against skimming attacks. Using picture-in-picture technology on the 19" screen increases the customers' awareness of what is going on around them. Enabling contactless, via cards or smart phones on the SelfServ 80 Series can eliminate the threat of card skimming entirely. These features - when combined with NCR Security software - allow NCR's 80 Series to protect you and your customers.











SelfServ Family



The NCR SelfServ Family is the world’s most complete ATM portfolio and number #1 brand with over 650,000 installs around the globe.
A configurable range of dispense, deposit and recycling ATMs designed to future proof your investment. These ATMs are the enabling platform to self-service reinvention and modernization for retail banks.  The newest addition to the range is the NCR SelfServ 80 series ATM family, aimed at the growing popularity of multi-function and intelligent deposit ATMs which now total over 1.1 million globally.



Multifunction ATMs




NCR SelfServ 81 - Multi-function Branch Assisted Service ATM





Your interactive banker is only one touch of the screen away from transforming your customer experience
The SelfServ 81’s user centered design enables financial institutions to connect with consumers within the branch. The SelfServ 81 is a new premium interior walk-up ATM from NCR featuring options including Interactive Teller for remote assisted service integration as well as Interactive Banker for in-person assistance compatibility. Designed for ease-of-use and delivering an exceptional assisted self-service experience, the SelfServ 81 is capable of handling the highest possible transaction volumes. The ATM creates the omni-channel experience by delivering reliable and secure access to cash for consumers. Modernize, innovate and bring the omni-channel experience to life with an ATM underpinned by NCR’s Media Handling 2.0 technology. The SelfServ 81’s human centered design enables financial institutions to drive positive customer experience.
Please note the SelfServ 81 is currently on a restricted phased regional release and not sold globally at this time.
Key features include:

Infinity Display – Supports multi-touch. 15” or 19” LCD
Audio - Enhanced high quality dynamic (Public/Private)
Supports “Picture in Picture” security
Flexible dispense, deposit and recycling configurations
Integrated contactless card reader (via card or smartphone)
Cameras - 3rd party consumer camera and optional cash slot camera enable
Integrated “flush” Skimming Protection Solution (SPS)
Supports NCR CxBanking SW platform
PC Core with Intel i5 processor.
Thermal Receipt/Journal Printer, options - Dual roll and 2ST
UPS (Uninterruptable Power Supply)
NCR Interactive Teller, remote assisted-service integrated.
NCR Interactive Banker, in person-assist compatible.
NCR Branch Transformation ready.




SelfServ 81 Branch Specific Datasheet
SelfServ 81 Interactive Teller Datasheet








NCR SelfServ 82 - Interior Walk-Up Multi-Function ATM





Reliability, usability and human-centred design. The SelfServ 82 is the key to creating a positive customer experiences.
The SelfServ 82 is a new premium interior walk-up ATM from NCR. Designed for ease-of-use and delivering an exceptional consumer experience and is capable of handling the highest possible transaction volumes. The SelfServ 82 delivers the omni-channel experience whilst ensuring reliable and secure access to cash for consumers.  Modernize, innovate and bring the omni-channel experience to life with an ATM underpinned by NCR’s Media Handling 2.0 technology. The SelfServ 82’s user centered design enables financial institutions to connect with consumers.
Key features of SelfServ 82 include:
Please note the SelfServ 82 is currently on a restricted phased regional release and not sold globally at this time.

Infinity Display – Supports multi-touch. 15” or 19” LCD
Audio - Enhanced high quality dynamic (Public/Private)
Supports “Picture in Picture” security
Flexible dispense, deposit and recycling configurations
Integrated contactless card reader (via card or smartphone)
Cameras - 3rd party consumer camera and optional cash slot camera enable
Integrated “flush” Skimming Protection Solution (SPS)
Supports NCR CxBanking SW platform
PC Core with Intel i5 processor.
Thermal Receipt/Journal Printer, options - Dual roll and 2ST
UPS (Uninterruptable Power Supply)




SelfServ 82 Datasheet







NCR SelfServ 84 Walk-up - Exterior Through the Wall Multi-Function ATM






Functional, efficient and convenient. The SelfServ 84's user centered design enables financial institutions to connect with consumers whenever and wherever they want.
The SelfServ 84 is a new premium exterior through the wall multi-function ATM from NCR. Designed for ease-of-use and delivering an exceptional consumer experience, the SelfServ 84 is capable of handling the highest possible transaction volumes. The ATM enables the omni-channel experience by delivering reliable and secure access to cash for consumers.  Modernize and innovate with an ATM underpinned by NCR’s Media Handling 2.0 technology. The SelfServ 84’s human centered design enables financial institutions to drive a positive customer experience. It keeps serving your customers with a wide range of transactions like mixed cash and check deposit and bill payment. Created to handle the severest of weather conditions. 
Please note the SelfServ 84 is currently on a restricted phased regional release and not sold globally at this time.
Key features include:

Infinity Display – Supports multi-touch. 15” or 19” LCD
Audio - Enhanced high quality dynamic (Public/Private)
Supports “Picture in Picture” security
Flexible dispense, deposit and recycling configurations
Integrated contactless card reader (via card or smartphone)
Cameras - 3rd party consumer camera and optional cash
										  slot camera enable
