SelfServ 84 Walk-up Datasheet








NCR SelfServ 84 Drive-up - Drive-Up Multi-Function ATM





Drive up, withdraw/pay in, drive away – The SelfServ 84 drive-up, complete with user friendly consumer interface.
The SelfServ 84 is a new premium exterior drive-up multi-function ATM from NCR. Designed for ease-of-use and delivering an exceptional consumer experience, the SelfServ 84 is capable of handling the highest possible transaction volumes. The ATM enables the omni-channel experience by delivering reliable and secure access to cash for consumers. Modernize and innovate with an ATM underpinned by NCR’s Media Handling 2.0 technology. The SelfServ 84’s human centered design enables financial institutions to drive positive customer experience. It keeps serving your customers with a wide range of transactions like mixed cash and check deposit and bill payment. Extreme weather is no challenge for the SelfServ 84 drive-up and its durable design ensures ease-of-use when operated from a vehicle. The user centered design helps bring your brand closer to and build connections with consumers – even from the comfort of their car. SelfServ ATMs continue to play a key role in the omni-channel experience by delivering reliable and secure access to cash for consumers. 
Key features include:

Infinity Display – Supports multi-touch. 15” or 19” LCD
Audio - Enhanced high quality dynamic (Public/Private)
Supports “Picture in Picture” security
Flexible dispense, deposit and recycling configurations
Integrated contactless card reader (via card or smartphone)
Cameras - 3rd party consumer camera and optional cash
									  slot camera enable
Integrated “flush” Skimming Protection Solution (SPS)
Supports NCR CxBanking SW platform
PC Core with Intel i5 processor.
Thermal Receipt/Journal Printer, options - Dual roll and 2ST
UPS (Uninterruptable Power Supply)




SelfServ 84 Drive-up Datasheet







NCR SelfServ 88 - Freestanding Drive-Up island Multi-Function ATM





The convenience of a 24/7 branch from the comfort of your vehicle.  Self-service ATM access, any time no matter what the weather.
The SelfServ 88 is a new premium exterior drive-up island ATM from NCR. Designed for ease-of-use and delivering an exceptional consumer experience, the SelfServ 88 is capable of handling the highest possible transaction volumes from the comfort of a consumer’s vehicle. The ATM enables the omni-channel experience by delivering reliable and secure access to cash for consumers. Modernize and innovate with an ATM underpinned by NCR’s Media Handling 2.0 technology. The SelfServ 88’s human centered design enables financial institutions to drive a positive customer experience – even when in a vehicle. It keeps serving your customers with a wide range of transactions like mixed cash and check deposit and bill payment. Offer your customers a wide range of ATM transactions without having to leave the car. Designed to cope with the severest of weather conditions, the SelfServ 88 keeps your customers comfortable while they withdraw cash, make deposits or pay bills. It doesn’t matter what type of vehicle your customers have. 
Please note the SelfServ 88 is currently on a restricted phased regional release (to North America only) and not sold globally at this time.
Key features include:

Infinity Display – Supports multi-touch. 15” or 19” LCD
Audio - Enhanced high quality dynamic (Public/Private)
Supports “Picture in Picture” security
Flexible dispense, deposit and recycling configurations
Integrated contactless card reader (via card or smartphone)
