The SelfServ 88 is a new premium exterior drive-up island ATM from NCR. Designed for ease-of-use and delivering an exceptional consumer experience, the SelfServ 88 is capable of handling the highest possible transaction volumes from the comfort of a consumer’s vehicle. The ATM enables the omni-channel experience by delivering reliable and secure access to cash for consumers. Modernize and innovate with an ATM underpinned by NCR’s Media Handling 2.0 technology. The SelfServ 88’s human centered design enables financial institutions to drive a positive customer experience – even when in a vehicle. It keeps serving your customers with a wide range of transactions like mixed cash and check deposit and bill payment. Offer your customers a wide range of ATM transactions without having to leave the car. Designed to cope with the severest of weather conditions, the SelfServ 88 keeps your customers comfortable while they withdraw cash, make deposits or pay bills. It doesn’t matter what type of vehicle your customers have. 
