Bill Nuti is Chairman and CEO of NCR Corporation. NCR is a leader in omni-channel solutions, enabling nearly 700 million transactions daily across retail, financial, travel, hospitality, telecom and technology, and small business. Bill is highly respected for his leadership skills and acclaimed for his vision and expertise in transforming and reinventing companies for sustainable and profitable growth. 



 






